<section class="premise" id="about" aria-labelledby="premise-heading">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="premise-inner">

      <div class="premise-text">
        <h2 class="premise-heading" id="premise-heading">
          Not an environmental argument. A common-sense upgrade.
        </h2>
        <p class="premise-body">
          The traditional American lawn is the most resource-intensive and least productive
          landscape in the country. A homeowner spends roughly twenty thousand dollars per
          acre over twenty years to maintain it. A native meadow costs three thousand over
          the same period, with no irrigation, no chemicals, and almost no weekly labor.
        </p>
        <p class="premise-body">
          The World's Best Office follows this movement at its most vivid &mdash; through
          the gardens of Sleepy Cat Farm, a thirteen-acre estate in Greenwich, Connecticut,
          the science of leading botanical institutions, and the homeowners who made the
          change and never looked back. It is not an environmental lecture. It is the story
          of a common-sense upgrade, told with cinematic ambition.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="premise-image">
        <img
          class="img-premise"
          src="/images/meadow-project-litchfield.webp"
          alt="Meadow Project, Litchfield County, Connecticut — native planting in progress"
          width="960"
          height="623"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .premise {
    padding: var(--space-24) 0;
  }

  .premise-inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
    gap: var(--space-16);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .premise-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .premise-body {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 65ch;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .premise-body:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .img-premise {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .premise-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .premise-image {
      order: -1;
    }
  }
</style>
